## Description {#details}

!cond(condition&#95;1: value1, ... , condition&#95;n: value) Selects the first value for which condition is true.

### isComplete() {#ae3bcc737ba443c50c9403d8cdcbcf1b0}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="bool CondOpInit::isComplete () const"
